  "body": "I will be sending a collection of PRs that are adding links to the defined terms in the terminology section.  This should help readability.\r\nI have specifically only linked uses of the term in text, not in code, to keep from making the Python code updates harder (guessing that the code is largely copied from the reference implementation).  I also did not include them in section titles in case that helps with ToC creation.\r\n\r\nI am submitting these changes as multiple independent PRs, one per term, in the hope that it will reduce merge conflicts.  I will link each one to this issue, so please don't close this issue until I comment that I have added all the related PRs I plan to.\r\n",
